USAGE OF SOURCE CODE
---------------------------------------

You may reference portions of the source code for educational purposes only
(e.g., learning how to create Terraria mods or similar software).

If you copy small code snippets for reference-based use, you must provide
clear credit to gl333pborg.

However, you may NOT:

- reuse or adapt large portions of the codebase,  
- create derivative works based on the code or assets,  
- redistribute the mod or any of its content,  
- publish modified or unmodified versions of the mod anywhere.


